nodes.text: Damian Farrell is an Irish puppeteer who worked as a creature and droid performer in the 2015 film Star Wars Episode VII The Force Awakens. He also played Munduri in the film. He also played the role of "Mimban Guard" in Solo: A Star Wars Story, which was released in 2018.
